{"data":[{"date":"13:24 14/06","title":"D\u00e0n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 \u0111ang b\u1ecb h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i \"c\u00e1m d\u1ed7\"","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/14/dan-tuyen-thu-anh-du-world-cup-2018-dang-bi-hang-loat-chan-dai-cam-do.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p s\u1ed1ng g\u1ea7n kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf World Cup \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tam s\u01b0.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Th\u00f4ng tin h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 Tinder cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u00ednh 10km c\u1ee7a n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u00f4 g\u00e1i t\u00f3c v\u00e0ng 21 tu\u1ed5i Alexis chia s\u1ebb \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm &quot;m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi World Cup k\u1ebft th\u00fac&quot;. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p 26 tu\u1ed5i Zhanna khoe \u1ea3nh th\u01b0\u1edbt tha v\u1edbi v\u00e1y tr\u1eafng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u00f4ng tin c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n tr\u00ean \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Tinder. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u c\u01b0 tr\u00fa t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n ForRestMix kh\u00f4ng xa.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 \u0111ang b\u1ecb h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i d\u1ee5 d\u1ed7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 \u0111ang b\u1ecb h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i d\u1ee5 d\u1ed7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/cc-7505-1528947857.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00e1c ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i g\u1ea7n kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u0103ng \u1ea3nh mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ea1n trai tr\u00ean \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Tinder. \u1ea2nh: NS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTinder ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf Nga - qu\u1ed1c gia c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 &quot;thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t&quot; c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng. Ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch gi\u1edbi t\u00ednh nam v\u00e0 n\u1eef l\u00ean t\u1edbi 11 tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. S\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng x\u1ea3y ra nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf Saint Petersburg, c\u00e1ch n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u00f4ng xa. \u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng h\u00e8n h\u00f2 cho ph\u00e9p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb GPS \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm b\u1ea1n kh\u00e1c gi\u1edbi g\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh nh\u1ea5t.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay, HLV Southgate kh\u00e1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ee3, b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i \u0111i c\u00f9ng. Tuy v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i ban h\u00e0nh l\u1ec7nh c\u1ea5m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn v\u01a1i tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh hay kh\u00f4ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&quot;Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Gareth mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o World Cup. M\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ean c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 g\u00e2y ra r\u1ee7i ro an ninh \u1edf Nga&quot;, m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin cho bi\u1ebft.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u1ede kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n, tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u00e0m h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o cao, c\u00e1ch ly \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u1edbi b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. Vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t an ninh c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra g\u1eaft gao b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i v\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb gi\u1eefa hai n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3613","checkdouble":"188472"},{"date":"17:36 14/06","title":"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League: \u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ngh\u0129 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/ha-noi-dai-thang-tai-vleague-da-den-luc-nghi-nghiem-tuc-ve-san-choi-chau-luc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua, c\u00e1c CLB Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn xem th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111em \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi m\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League, xem ch\u1eebng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 AFC Cup.</h2><h2>B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng th\u1ee5t l\u00f9i v\u00ec t\u01b0 duy c\u0169</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra &lsquo;m\u1eb7n&rsquo; v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea5p CLB nh\u01b0 AFC Champions League hay AFC Cup m\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 chinh chi\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t l\u00fac tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i AFC Cup n\u0103m nay, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t SLNA thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c hay \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean nh\u01b0ng c\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed1i, s\u1ef1 h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 khi h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League</span>.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i V-League \u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 AFC Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i V-League \u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 AFC Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/30/Ha-Noi-bat-bai-tai-V-League-Da-den-luc-nghi-ve-AFC-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 SLNA \u0111\u1ec1u d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng AFC Cup 2018.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1edbm bu\u00f4ng AFC Cup l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn hai CLB Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 SLNA \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed5i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong khu v\u1ef1c, d\u00f9 x\u00e9t tr\u00ean b\u00ecnh di\u1ec7n \u0110TQG th\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1 tai h\u1ea1i l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t khi ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng th\u1ee5t l\u00f9i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00ec n\u1ebfp suy ngh\u0129 c\u0169. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n th\u1eddi m\u1ed9t B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eebng tung ho\u00e0nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Champions League hay AFC Cup, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t nh\u1ee3t nh\u1ea1t c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1ea7m khu v\u1ef1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ec7m c\u1eadn c\u00e1c n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 nh\u01b0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Trung Qu\u1ed1c, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Iran,&hellip; v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ea1ng 8 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng th\u1ee9 19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, x\u1ebfp d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ea3 Malaysia hay Philippines, hai qu\u1ed1c gia v\u1ed1n \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean ti\u1ebfng vang t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u00e0o ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng AFC Cup, ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea1ng 1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 AFC Champions League.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"AFC Club Ranking\" title=\"AFC Club Ranking\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Thai-Lan-vuot-Australia-bo-xa-Viet-Nam-tren-BXH-chau-a-vn-02-1528445203-width709height633.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5p \u1edf c\u1ea5p CLB</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u0169ng t\u1eebng su\u00fdt v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng AFC Cup 2017 v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ebb tre \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, tuy nhi\u00ean sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd 2-6 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ceres-Negros, t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 duy nh\u1ea5t b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong tay h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay, v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League 2018, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng AFC Cup 2019. V\u00e0 thi\u1ebft ngh\u0129 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eb1m gi\u00fap b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00e2ng cao th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c c\u1ea5p CLB.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i AFC Cup l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/dtqg-c292-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span> t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1, c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng&nbsp;\u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 chuy\u1ec3n m\u00ecnh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u01a1n, tin d\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, hoa m\u0129 h\u01a1n, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m g\u00ec s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean khi m\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, CLB HAGL v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u0169ng gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi th\u1ed1 \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ha Noi vs Than Quang Ninh Oseni\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh Oseni\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/oseni-5816-1528894838_600x0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i V-League nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang \u1edf trong \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng b\u1ea7u r\u1ee7ng r\u1ec9nh v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ee9ng sau ch\u1ed1ng l\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf AFC Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 t\u00edch l\u0169y ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c, kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 CLB v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0110TQG sau n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup 2019 v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2026.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng \u0111ang chung tay x\u00e2y \u0111\u1eafp \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam-c168-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span> t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u01b0\u01a1n cao nh\u1eb1m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ec7m c\u1eadn tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/13/Ha-Noi-4-1-Quang-Ninh.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-thua-quang-nam-tat-ca-da-nam-trong-toan-tinh-cua-bau-duc-168-188433.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/hagl-thua-quang-nam-tat-ca-da-nam-trong-toan-tinh-cua-bau-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-thua-quang-nam-tat-ca-da-nam-trong-toan-tinh-cua-bau-duc-168-188433.html\">HAGL thua Qu\u1ea3ng Nam: T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m trong toan t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c</span><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecf ra bi quan v\u1ec1 ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL sau tr\u1eadn thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i qua t\u1ea1i Pleiku. Tuy nhi\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-fc-mung-sinh-nhat-tuoi-12-day-y-nghia-291-188432.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/ha-noi-fc-mung-sinh-nhat-tuoi-12-day-y-nghia.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-fc-mung-sinh-nhat-tuoi-12-day-y-nghia-291-188432.html\">Ch\u00f9m \u1ea3nh: M\u00e0n ch\u00fac m\u1eebng sinh nh\u1eadt tu\u1ed5i 12 c\u1ef1c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC</span><br>\r\nH\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC m\u1eebng sinh nh\u1eadt tu\u1ed5i 12 \u0111\u1ea7y \u00fd ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi m\u00e0n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng phu c\u1ee7a h\u1ed9i c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ha-noi-nhan-thuong-khung-tu-bau-hien-sau-chien-tich-bat-bai-o-luot-di-168-188427.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/16/ha-noi-nhan-thuong-khung-tu-bau-hien-sau-chien-tich-bat-bai-o-luot-di.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ha-noi-nhan-thuong-khung-tu-bau-hien-sau-chien-tich-bat-bai-o-luot-di-168-188427.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u1eadn th\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u1ee7ng t\u1eeb b\u1ea7u Hi\u1ec3n sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1ea7u Hi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n khen ng\u1ee3i v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edfng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p>Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3612","checkdouble":"188434"},{"date":"15:26 14/06","title":"Tr\u1eadn B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs SLNA kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n, ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/tran-binh-duong-vs-slna-khong-bi-hoan-phai-doi-dia-diem.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs SLNA v\u1eabn s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 17/6 nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb s\u00e2n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng sang s\u00e2n Vinh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u trong n\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs SLNA kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec l\u00fd do an ninh, T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c L\u00ea H\u1ed3ng C\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eedi c\u00f4ng v\u0103n \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00f9i ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs SLNA t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y theo l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 17/6, ph\u00eda B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00f9i ng\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 1/9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tran Binh Duong vs SLNA van se dien ra vao ngay 17/6.\" title=\"Tr\u1eadn B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs SLNA v\u1eabn s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 17/6.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/tran-binh-duong-vs-slna-khong-bi-hoan-phai-doi-dia-diem.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Tr\u1eadn B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs SLNA v\u1eabn s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 17/6.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fd do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1edfi nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch quan khi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c b\u00ean, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb s\u00e2n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng sang s\u00e2n Vinh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u trong n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eafc d\u0129 b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a SLNA \u0111\u1ebfn hai tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a SLNA v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-0. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u1edbi 5 h\u00f2a, 1 thua.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 lo l\u1eafng khi th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn c\u00f3 \u00edt th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn b\u1edfi \u1edf v\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0o TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn ba tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn khi g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 g\u1ed3m SLNA (17/6), Thanh H\u00f3a (22/6) v\u00e0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a (26/6). B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd di chuy\u1ec3n ra s\u00e2n Vinh v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 15/6 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 hai ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/tran-binh-duong-vs-slna-co-the-bi-hoan-291-188389.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/tran-binh-duong-vs-slna-co-the-bi-hoan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/tran-binh-duong-vs-slna-co-the-bi-hoan-291-188389.html\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs SLNA t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n</span><br>\r\nTheo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng L\u00ea H\u1ed3ng C\u01b0\u1eddng, tr\u1eadn B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs SLNA c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 9 v\u00ec m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do kh\u00e1ch quan.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3611","checkdouble":"188478"},{"date":"15:47 14/06","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng sau tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/30/cong-phuong-trai-long-sau-tran-thua-truoc-quang-nam.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i qua 13/6.</h2><h2>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng sau tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 13 V-League di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i qua 13/6, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam sau tr\u1eadn thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HAGL l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau c\u00fa s\u00fat xa hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 tung ra pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m uy l\u1ef1c khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch d\u00f9 bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ebft c\u1ee1 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng sau tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng sau tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/cong-phuong-trai-long-sau-tran-thua-truoc-quang-nam.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: \"H\u00f4m nay to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t khi c\u00f3 hai l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n. Nh\u01b0ng V.League 2018 c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, HAGL s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 mong \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 Pleiku\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, ngo\u00e0i pha m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, anh c\u0169ng mang v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u1ee7a HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i: \u201cC\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng v\u00ec nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. H\u00f4m nay Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n. Hy v\u1ecdng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef v\u1eefng phong \u0111\u1ed9\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn HAGL m\u1ea5t m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i \u2018l\u00e0nh \u00edt, d\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u\u2019 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\u00a0<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-thua-quang-nam-tat-ca-da-nam-trong-toan-tinh-cua-bau-duc-168-188433.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/hagl-thua-quang-nam-tat-ca-da-nam-trong-toan-tinh-cua-bau-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-thua-quang-nam-tat-ca-da-nam-trong-toan-tinh-cua-bau-duc-168-188433.html\">HAGL thua Qu\u1ea3ng Nam: T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m trong toan t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c</span><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecf ra bi quan v\u1ec1 ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL sau tr\u1eadn thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i qua t\u1ea1i Pleiku. Tuy nhi\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-23-quang-nam-cong-lam-thu-pha-168-188422.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-23-quang-nam-cong-lam-thu-pha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-23-quang-nam-cong-lam-thu-pha-168-188422.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam: C\u00f4ng l\u00e0m, th\u1ee7 ph\u00e1</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, CLB HAGL v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3610","checkdouble":"188480"},{"date":"12:41 14/06","title":"Griezmann l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai... nh\u01b0 phim bom t\u1ea5n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/27/griezmann-len-ke-hoach-thong-bao-tuong-lai-nhu-phim-bom-tan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griemann th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ph\u1ea3i d\u1eddi l\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nGriezmann \u00fap m\u1edf t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&quot;T\u00f4i xin l\u1ed7i, nh\u01b0ng h\u00f4m nay kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u00e0y t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng&quot; </strong>- nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Griezmann trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, d\u00f9 anh t\u1eebng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u1eddi gian, khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn 16/6, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 ngay tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 &quot;vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb&quot;a m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i (&quot;th\u1ea3 th\u00ednh&quot; M.U nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i), v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1eafc l\u1ea1i sai l\u1ea7m m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ch\u1eeba l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng lui cho m\u00ecnh. Griezmann kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh c\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Atletico Madrid nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1o tin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antoine Griemann th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai nh\u01b0 phim bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Antoine Griemann th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai nh\u01b0 phim bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/Antoine-Griemann-thong-bao-tuong-lai-nhu-phim-bom-tan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Griezmann th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ki\u1ec3u n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f4i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed, Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm ra gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, <strong>anh \u0111\u00e3 quay... 2 \u0111o\u1ea1n video \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 tr\u00f9 trong m\u1ecdi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p</strong>, 1 clip \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico, c\u00f2n 1 clip tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf, th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 Barcelona. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Barca, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p 2 b\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3, anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch Antoine Griezmann th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111i\u1ec7n \u1ea3nh bom t\u1ea5n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i b\u1ed9 phim trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n b\u1eaft di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean quay nhi\u1ec1u \u0111o\u1ea1n k\u1ebft kh\u00e1c nhau. T\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh c\u00e1c di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 phim m\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griezmann, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00e1nh b\u00e1o ch\u00ed c\u0169ng n\u00ean ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y. B\u1edfi m\u1ed9t l\u1ebd \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau m\u00f9a h\u00e8.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-la-dai-ca-o-tuyen-phap-421-188449.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/griezmann-la-dai-ca-o-tuyen-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-la-dai-ca-o-tuyen-phap-421-188449.html\">Griezmann l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i ca \u1edf tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra \u00edt ng\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh - sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-tuyen-phap-bao-tin-buon-cho-mu-vu-griezmann-184-188294.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/10/hlv-tuyen-phap-bao-tin-buon-cho-mu-vu-griezmann.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-tuyen-phap-bao-tin-buon-cho-mu-vu-griezmann-184-188294.html\">HLV tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho MU v\u1ee5 Griezmann</span><br>\r\nHLV Didier Deschamps kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Antoine Griezmann s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Premier League \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho MU.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh - TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3609","checkdouble":"188470"},{"date":"14:52 14/06","title":"Sadio Mane c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/27/sadio-mane-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real Madrid mua Sadio Mane th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Anfield \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m Mane</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, t\u1edd Don Balon c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-bat-ngo-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-voi-sao-khung-liverpool-180-187771.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sadio Mane</span> c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Los Blancos nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n Real Madrid mua Sadio Mane th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n Real Madrid mua Sadio Mane th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Khong-co-chuyen-Real-Madrid-mua-Sadio-Mane-thanh-cong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m Sadio Mane&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mane ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Firmino v\u00e0 Salah h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Mane ghi 20 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 8 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 Champions League.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal, s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Liverpool nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec The Kop b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb Southampton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mane t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real Madrid mua Sadio Mane th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Anfield \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Ings phat bieu ve Sadio Mane\" title=\"Danny Ings ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sadio Mane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/20/Jurgen-Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Sadio-Mane-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sadio Mane h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m n\u1eefa v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, nh\u01b0ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Anfield&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Hi\u1ec7n t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0110T Senegal tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng Liverpool chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede World Cup 2018, Senegal n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng H v\u1edbi Ba Lan, Colombia v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt b\u1ea3n. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3608","checkdouble":"188475"},{"date":"17:24 14/06","title":"\"Judas\" Lopetegui mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/22/judas-lopetegui-muoi-mat-tro-lai-tay-ban-nha-chuan-bi-ra-mat-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ngay sau khi nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1t sa th\u1ea3i, HLV Julen Lopetegui tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nLopetegui b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Scandal c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018. V\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n x\u1ee9 b\u00f2 t\u00f3t l\u1ea1i tr\u1ea3m t\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u1ec9 1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, HLV Lopetegui d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 v\u1eeba m\u1edbi gia h\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, ph\u00eda Real c\u0169ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup, v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Luis Rubiales kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi nh\u1eadn tin sa th\u1ea3i, Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 thu x\u1ebfp h\u00e0nh l\u00fd v\u00e0 l\u00ean s\u00e2n bay Krasnodar tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 51 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u00f4ng v\u1eabn mong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p m\u1ecdi r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i do ch\u00ednh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n g\u00e2y ra. HLV n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng mong r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/lop.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Lopetegui tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y&rdquo; &ndash; Lopetegui k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, thay th\u1ebf HLV n\u00e0y d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Fernando Hierro, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 n\u1eafm \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha trong tr\u1eadn derby b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia, sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 2 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Iran v\u00e0 Ma R\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda &ldquo;t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3&rdquo; Lopetegui tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n. D\u00f9 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eafc d\u0129 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1eb7t ra, nh\u01b0ng Los Blancos s\u1ebd t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui ngay h\u00f4m nay (t\u1ed1i mu\u1ed9n theo gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-co-nguy-co-bao-dong-sau-khi-lopetegui-ra-di-421-188457.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/10/cay-dang-roi-trai-tbn-lopetegui-nhan-cac-hoc-tro-bien-noi-dau-thanh-dong-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-co-nguy-co-bao-dong-sau-khi-lopetegui-ra-di-421-188457.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng sau khi Lopetegui ra \u0111i?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u1ea5n an d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh li\u1ec1u l\u0129nh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c World Cup...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vu-be-boi-lopetegui-tbn-het-cach-real-madrid-phai-chiu-trach-nhiem-421-188447.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/vu-be-boi-lopetegui-tbn-het-cach-real-madrid-phai-chiu-trach-nhiem.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vu-be-boi-lopetegui-tbn-het-cach-real-madrid-phai-chiu-trach-nhiem-421-188447.html\">V\u1ee5 b\u00ea b\u1ed1i Lopetegui: TBN h\u1ebft c\u00e1ch, Real Madrid ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m</span><br>\r\nHLV Sam Allardyce \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh r\u1eafn m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00fang m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3607","checkdouble":"188486"},{"date":"15:09 14/06","title":"Ajax ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 18 tu\u1ed5i cho Man City v\u00e0 Tottenham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/15/ajax-chot-gia-ban-trung-ve-18-tuoi-cho-man-city-va-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ajax b\u00e1n Matthijs de Ligt n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, hi\u1ec7n Man City v\u00e0 Tottenham l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City v\u00e0 Tottenham quan t\u00e2m De Ligt</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Matthijs de Ligt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0 Lan. Ng\u00f4i sao 18 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ajax.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ajax b\u00e1n Matthijs de Ligt v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ajax b\u00e1n Matthijs de Ligt v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/ajax-chot-gia-ban-trung-ve-18-tuoi-cho-man-city-va-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham v\u00e0 Man City quan t\u00e2m Matthijs De Ligt</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1999 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu trung v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng t\u1ed1t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao. De Ligt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0 Lan.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t. \u1ede Anh, Man City v\u00e0 Tottenham quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1999. Man xanh nh\u1eafm De Ligt nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Kompany, Spurs mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i thay Toby Alderweireld.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ajax ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n De Ligt</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ajax b\u00e1n Matthijs de Ligt n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham chi 50 trieu bang mua Matthijs de Ligt\" title=\"Tottenham chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Matthijs de Ligt\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/man-city-va-tottenham-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-vu-hau-ve-50-trieu-bang.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ajax ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Matthijs de Ligt v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Ajax \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 Man City c\u00f3 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man xanh ho\u1eb7c Spurs b\u1ecf th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1999 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, De Ligt ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. N\u0103m nay 18 tu\u1ed5i, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Tottenham ho\u1eb7c Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1edf d\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 Lan bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 b\u1edfi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-va-tottenham-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-vu-hau-ve-50-trieu-bang-172-186013.html\" target=\"_blank\">De Ligt mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Ajax</span>, anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3606","checkdouble":"188476"},{"date":"15:43 14/06","title":"Premier League ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/7/premier-league-chinh-thuc-cong-bo-lich-thi-dau-mua-giai-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c Premier League \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. Arsenal c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 vui c\u01b0\u1eddi cho n\u1ed5i khi ph\u1ea3i m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ebfn hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Premier League 2018/19 s\u1ebd khai m\u1ea1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i h\u01a1n b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Arsenal vs Man City tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Emirates. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Unai Emery tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 sau 22 n\u0103m gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 Arsene Wenger.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan cho Arsenal khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Premier League 201819 Arsenal vs Man City v\u00f2ng 1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Premier League 201819 Arsenal vs Man City v\u00f2ng 1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Lich-thi-dau-Premier-League-201819-Arsenal-vs-Man-City-vong-1-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Arsenal vs Man City ng\u00e0y v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t khi sang ngay v\u00f2ng th\u1ee9 hai, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha (Unai Emery) s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn derby London l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Arsenal vs Man City, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong nh\u00f3m Big Six \u0111\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1ec5 th\u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng 4 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecd c\u0169ng thu\u1ed9c d\u1ea1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c. Man Utd v\u00e0 Liverpool l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Leicester v\u00e0 West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, trong khi Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Huddersfield v\u00e0 Newcastle.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tottenham s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c khai s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1edbi 62 ngh\u00ecn ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ed3i g\u1eb7p t\u00e2n binh Fulham \u1edf v\u00f2ng hai nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfn tr\u00ecnh thi c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Liverpool v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, th\u00e1ng 12 s\u1ebd ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn derby n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng, bao g\u1ed3m derby Merseyside (Liverpool vs Everton), derby B\u1eafc London (Arsenal vs Tottenham), derby Manchester (Man Utd vs Man City) v\u00e0 derby n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh (Man Utd vs Liverpool).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Premier League 2018/19 \u2013 V\u00f2ng 1 (11-12/8/2018):<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich thi dau Premier League 2018/19 - Vong 1\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Premier League 2018/19 - V\u00f2ng 1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/PL_Fixtures_Lead.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Premier League 2018/19 - V\u00f2ng 1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3605","checkdouble":"188479"},{"date":"10:20 14/06","title":"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018: H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/13/5-diem-nhan-sau-luot-di-vleague-2018-ha-noi-va-mot-nua-con-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i sau v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 13 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i qua 13/6. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1eafng \u0111\u1ecdng l\u1ea1i sau n\u1eeda ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>1. S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u1ea1i + nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng d\u00e0n sao n\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb trung, \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi 13 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t \u0111a d\u1ea1ng, t\u1eeb t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng trung l\u1ed9, \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t hay c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ed3ng bi\u00ean. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Oseni \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 13 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/13 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i 13 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/tong-hop-ha-noi-41-quang-ninh-vong-13-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i\u00a0</em><i>l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 huy b\u1edfi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1ed3m Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i V-League, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn cho kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u00fang 8 m\u00f9a t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, \u00edt s\u1ed1 trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tham d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 CLB \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng nh\u1ea5t V-League v\u1edbi 36 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ch\u1ec9 v\u1eady th\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. C\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1ed1p 3<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi hai m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch lu\u00f4n di\u1ec5n ra c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng th\u00ec t\u1ea1i V-League 2018, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang \u20181 m\u00ecnh, 1 ng\u1ef1a\u2019 ti\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch. Tuy nhi\u00ean cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 3 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111ang t\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 v\u1edbi 20 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nh\u01b0ng kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 10 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m. X\u1ebfp gi\u1eefa Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a v\u00e0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (19 \u0111i\u1ec3m), H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng (19), C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 (19), Qu\u1ea3ng Nam (19), HAGL (17), Thanh H\u00f3a (16), \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng (16).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t s\u00edt sao nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn \u1edf n\u1eeda ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, HAGL nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, Thanh H\u00f3a hay Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00fd gi\u00e1. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1ed1p gi\u1eefa v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ho-da-noi-gi-sau-tran-slna-10-hai-phong-168-188429.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/ho-da-noi-gi-sau-tran-slna-10-hai-phong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ho-da-noi-gi-sau-tran-slna-10-hai-phong-168-188429.html\">HLV hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn SLNA 1-0 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng?</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng trong khi \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft \u01a1n t\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V x\u1ee9...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>3. N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 4-1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed l\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft s\u1edbm t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 13, v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 11 \u0111i\u1ec3m, V-League n\u0103m nay c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn trong c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ai s\u1ebd xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m sau.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 SLNA, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ecfng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd nh\u1ea5t cho su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 13, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, 3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 8 tr\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam nhen nh\u00f3m hy v\u1ecdng tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nam Dinh vs Sai Gon FC\" title=\"Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/nam-dinh-1-0-sai-gon-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh nhen nh\u00f3m l\u1ea1i hy v\u1ecdng tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh gi\u00fap Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n m\u01a1 t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V-League 2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1eadn thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ed1i qua 13/6 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam th\u1eafng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00f3t b\u1ea3ng r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0nh cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, khi m\u00e0 \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t \u2018c\u1ee9ng\u2019. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i HAGL \u1edf v\u00f2ng 15. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh m\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 16, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Vinh c\u1ee7a SLNA. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 12 v\u1edbi 11 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y S\u00e0i G\u00f2n g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chung ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh v\u1edbi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, SLNA c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung h\u01a1n n\u1eefa cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi hai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nam-dinh-co-chien-thang-dau-tay-tren-san-nha-hlv-sai-gon-chi-uoc-1-dieu-168-188430.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/nam-dinh-co-chien-thang-dau-tay-tren-san-nha-hlv-sai-gon-chi-uoc-1-dieu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nam-dinh-co-chien-thang-dau-tay-tren-san-nha-hlv-sai-gon-chi-uoc-1-dieu-168-188430.html\">CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, HLV S\u00e0i G\u00f2n ch\u1ec9 \u01b0\u1edbc 1 \u0111i\u1ec1u</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV S\u00e0i G\u00f2n Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm g\u1eb7p tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. S\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00f2ng 13 V-League di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn, \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3. Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea t\u1eeb BTC, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 54 ng\u00e0n kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed7 v\u0169 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1edbi 13 ngh\u00ecn kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3. S\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ngu\u1ed9i b\u1edbt s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng v\u1eabn v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec v\u1edbi 12 ngh\u00ecn, ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 s\u00e2n Pleiku (HAGL) 10 ngh\u00ecn v\u00e0 s\u00e2n Thanh H\u00f3a 7 ngh\u00ecn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p. Kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4ng h\u01a1n, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mang l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng ngu\u1ed3n thu cho c\u00e1c CLB m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng d\u1ea7n m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng chung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng V-League 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac CDV Ha Noi da chuan bi rat cong phu de mung sinh nhat tuoi 12 cua CLB.\" title=\"C\u00e1c C\u0110V H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng phu \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eebng sinh nh\u1eadt tu\u1ed5i 12 c\u1ee7a CLB.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/IMG_0660_resize.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>S\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi CLB\u00a0H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>5. C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau v\u1ee5 \u1ed3n \u00e0o li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n 19-8 gi\u1eefa Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs HAGL t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 7, nh\u00ecn chung c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018. Trong th\u1eddi gian qua \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u2018v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en\u2019 n\u00e0o b\u1ecb x\u1eed l\u00fd k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt d\u00f9 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i t\u1ed1t d\u1ea7n l\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u m\u1eebng v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Khi s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean c\u00e1c s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cho t\u1edbi NHM c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn h\u01a1n cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 t\u1ed1t d\u1ea7n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League</span> tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/13/Ha-Noi-4-1-Quang-Ninh.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-thua-quang-nam-tat-ca-da-nam-trong-toan-tinh-cua-bau-duc-168-188433.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/hagl-thua-quang-nam-tat-ca-da-nam-trong-toan-tinh-cua-bau-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-thua-quang-nam-tat-ca-da-nam-trong-toan-tinh-cua-bau-duc-168-188433.html\">HAGL thua Qu\u1ea3ng Nam: T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m trong toan t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c</span><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecf ra bi quan v\u1ec1 ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL sau tr\u1eadn thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i qua t\u1ea1i Pleiku. Tuy nhi\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-188425.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/9/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-188425.html\">HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam?</span><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cho l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u V-League t\u1eeb BTC gi\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-23-quang-nam-cong-lam-thu-pha-168-188422.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-23-quang-nam-cong-lam-thu-pha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-23-quang-nam-cong-lam-thu-pha-168-188422.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam: C\u00f4ng l\u00e0m, th\u1ee7 ph\u00e1</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, CLB HAGL v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-khang-dinh-ha-noi-se-vo-dich-291-188426.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-khang-dinh-ha-noi-se-vo-dich.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-khang-dinh-ha-noi-se-vo-dich-291-188426.html\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2018</span><br>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch khi m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 v\u1edbi hai ch\u1eef kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3604","checkdouble":"188461"},{"date":"09:05 14/06","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a MU gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Atletico","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/1/gimenez-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-atletico.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Jose Gimenez \u0111\u00e3 cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 5 n\u0103m.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gimenez gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Atletico</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gimenez gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Atletico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gimenez gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Atletico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/1/gimenez-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-atletico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gimenez gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Atletico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Gimenez tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng 6/2020. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Atletico \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00eam 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ecdi tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i. Man United v\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/gimenez-phat-bieu-ve-real-180-188047.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Gimenez</span> trong v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gimenez \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 134 l\u1ea7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Atletico k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Rojiblancos v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013. Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Diego Godin t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gimenez n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Atletico t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2023, Gimenez vui m\u1eebng chia s\u1ebb:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bi\u1ebft \u01a1n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00e0 CLB \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh cho t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1edbi v\u00e0 th\u1eadt vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho d\u1ef1 \u00e1n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;Ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a cho m\u1ecdi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 \u1edf nh\u00e0. N\u00ean t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m \u01a1n m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o t\u00f4i&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gimenez c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Uruguay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Oscar Tabarez s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00f9ng Ai C\u1eadp, Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga cho m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Atletico:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bat-ngo-nham-hau-ve-atletico-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-188404.html\">Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1eafm h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Atletico n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/dai-gia-la-liga-chinh-thuc-so-huu-thomas-lemar-voi-gia-khung-180-188349.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i gia La Liga ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu Thomas Lemar v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3603","checkdouble":"188445"},{"date":"09:08 14/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 14/6: Real s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng De Gea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/21/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-146-real-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-de-gea-voi-gia-khong-tuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 14/6.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng De Gea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 146 Real s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng De Gea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 146 Real s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng De Gea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-146-Real-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-De-Gea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua De gea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Manchester Evening News, Real Madrid \u0111ang t\u1ef1 tin chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David de Gea c\u1ee7a MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mbappe: &quot;Griezmann s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018&quot;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kylian Mbappe ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antoine Griezmann, ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i tin r\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Atletico Madrid s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ajax ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n De Ligt v\u00e0 De Jong</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mundo Deportivo, Ajax \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Matthijs de Ligt v\u00e0 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Frenkie De Jong.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Martial mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham chi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Grealish\" title=\"Jack Grealish\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/tottenham-muon-vuot-mat-mu-vu-sao-aston-villa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sky Sports News, Tottenham c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Villa Park c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ander Herrera mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Mourinho v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo The Sun, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ander Herrera s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Dortmund mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 sao Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Dortmund \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Golovin\" title=\"Chelsea mua Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/17/juventus-sap-co-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-mu-va-arsenal.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Golovin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Calciomercato.com kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Alexsandar Golovin t\u1eeb Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nice mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Man City</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Daily Mail, Nice l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Joe Hart c\u1ee7a Man City, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3602","checkdouble":"188448"},{"date":"09:58 14/06","title":"Ander Herrera mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p Mourinho nh\u1eb1m l\u00e0m r\u00f5 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/19/ander-herrera-muon-gap-mourinho-nham-lam-ro-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ander Herrera s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ander Herrera c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ander Herrera th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u cho M.U. \u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, M.U \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Fred v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ander Herrera \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ander Herrera \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/19/Tuong-lai-Ander-Herrera-duoc-quyet-dinh-sau-cuoc-gap-voi-Mourinho-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Herrera c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Herrera \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 4 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, sau Matic, Pogba v\u00e0 Fred. N\u1ebfu Fellaini \u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 5 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Mourinho \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Herrera ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Inter Milan v\u00e0 Atletico Madrid l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989. Mirror m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh AC Milan gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Herrera, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Herrera mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p Mourinho ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/voi-su-co-mat-cua-fred-ander-herrera-co-roi-mu-172-188212.html\" target=\"_blank\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ander Herrera</span> s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ander Herrera \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ander Herrera \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/19/ander-herrera-muon-gap-mourinho-nham-lam-ro-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Herrera mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p Mourinho ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Herrera mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Mourinho hay kh\u00f4ng. N\u1ebfu \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989, anh mu\u1ed1n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-khung-psg-172-188458.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/24/mu-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-khung-psg.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-khung-psg-172-188458.html\">MU nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Marco Verratti th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Tuchel v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu Mourinho kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Bilbao, anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi cho m\u00ecnh. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Herrera mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, song n\u1ebfu n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Mourinho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Herrera v\u1edbi M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 6 n\u0103m 2019, song \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o cho th\u1ea5y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3601","checkdouble":"188454"}]}